{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake-auto, cv-bridge, depthai-ros-msgs, image-transport, message-filters, opencv, rclcpp, rclcpp-components, sensor-msgs, vision-msgs, visualization-msgs }:
